Megamouth

large-scale text mining of marine science literature

https://github.com/OC-NTNU/megamouth

Copyright Erwin Marsi
2016



--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

baleen-python and all its dependencies


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Setup
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Install baleen-python (including all of its dependencies) and activate it
   (megamouth uses the same virtual Python environment as baleen-python).
   See https://github.com/OC-NTNU/baleen-python


2. Clone git repos

	$ git clone https://github.com/OC-NTNU/megamouth.git


3. Setup Megamouth environment with

    $ source setup_env.sh


4. Copy scripts/local-sample.ini to scripts/local.ini.
   Modify the paths in local.ini acording to your local setup.



--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Run
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	$ cd scripts
	$ ./megamouth-abs.py run-all


